These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: lettuce, strawberry, grapes, papaya, cherry, pepper, avocado
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, canadian, british, pakistani, turkish
 1. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating papaya is not the pakistani##6
 3. the australian is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
 6. the australian is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the egyptian##7
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the canadian is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the italian##7
10. the italian is on the left or right of the australian##3
11. the british is on the far left##1
12. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
13. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
14. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
15. the person eating cherry is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | grapes    | lettuce    | strawberry | pepper | papaya | cherry    | avocado |
| Nationality   | british | australian | italian  | pakistani   | canadian    | egyptian | turkish |

