.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, corn, lettuce, lime, spinach, cranberry, pepper
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, card-games, photography, collecting, drawing, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person eating pepper and the person eating corn##7
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is the person eating lime##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the person eating garlic is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 6. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person eating lime and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
 7. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the person eating lime and the person eating corn##7
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
10. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person eating pepper##6
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person eating lime##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | pepper  | lettuce | cranberry | lime | garlic     | spinach | corn  |
| Hobby   | card-games | drawing | board-games  | writing  | collecting | photography      | filmmaking |

