 3. the fan of dubstep is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
 4. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 5. the fan of disco is between the fan of salsa and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
 6. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of pop##7
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the fan of disco##6
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
15. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
16. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the fan of salsa##6
17. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
18. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
19. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5

.:: Answer ::.
