 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 5. the person who's sport is rollering is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the train##7
 8. the person who's sport is rollering is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
10. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is climbing##7
12. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
13. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
14. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
15. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
16. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
