 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 6. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the owner of the rat is not the person watching sports movies##6
10. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
11. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
12. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
